{"tid":808631,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"冇同過MK妹拍拖,人生根本唔完滿........","createTime":"2018-09-06T13:10:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-06T16:27:18.000Z","uid":58335,"like":43,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"e33ca03fade7c67b992e1d8d0a8b4eba71d27e80","tid":808631,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T13:10:16.000Z","msg":"港女未必識洗衫煮飯(講緊就算冇野做個D)<br />\n但MK妹就唔同,我見好多MK妹比人搞大左個肚<br />\n反而好踏實做人<br />\n相夫教子,仲會去街市買餸煮飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n港女未必肯為愛情付出,只貪錢愛自己<br />\n但MK妹就唔同,我見好多MK妹都跟個垃圾冇出色MK仔<br />\n只少以佢地個靚樣,絕對可以搵個好過MK仔唔少既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n港女未必肯過簡單生活,日日掛住食咩Lady M,飲閪茶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但MK妹就唔同,我見好多MK妹食個M記,是但食個茶記已經好開心<br />\n生活好簡單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果你一生都冇同過MK妹拍拖<br />\n只同過港女拍拖結婚既話<br />\n咁你人生已經玩完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01b80495f4777b31edd84bedce45460bcb696d98","tid":808631,"uid":169116,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T13:11:59.000Z","msg":"首先你唔係MK仔點溝得到MK妹呀"},{"pid":"151cd77cde8dfd17f4746cef3194d50a8b6e13ca","tid":808631,"uid":24234,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T13:12:17.000Z","msg":"同意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"603dfcc02d4657bfbcf895941770bf6c91d3d8db","tid":808631,"uid":58335,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"01b80495f4777b31edd84bedce45460bcb696d98","tid":808631,"uid":169116,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T13:11:59.000Z","msg":"首先你唔係MK仔點溝得到MK妹呀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T13:14:43.000Z","msg":"Mk妹好簡單<br />\n只要你對佢地好D,佢地就好易愛上你架你<img src=\"/assets/f